title: Can you match these Alabama beer labels to their brewery? Take our quiz.
text:
Comments 
Whether you are a macrobrewery fan or only drink local beer, you probably have heard that Alabama has a burgeoning brewery scene. 
We want to test how well you know your Alabama beer labels. Try our quiz below, and share with your friends to compare your knowledge of Alabama beers. 
And don't forget: Wednesday is the last day to vote for your favorite signature beer in our poll. RELATED :
